u.s. lend sudan 57 mln dlr for wheat purchas the u.s. is to lend sudan 57 mln dlr to buy 309,000 tonn of wheat and 73,000 tonn of wheat flour , accord to an agreement sign here . under the agreement sudan will receiv 50 mln dlr for the commod and the rest for sea transport . the loan is repay in 40 year , includ a 10-year grace period . interest will be two pct for the grace period and three pct over the repay period of 30 year .